title: Five-star cookies
ingredients: ['50 g (1¾ oz) hazelnuts, finely chopped', '50 g (1¾ oz) sunflower seeds, finely chopped', '50 g (1¾ oz) ready-to-eat dried apricots, finely chopped', '50 g (1¾ oz) stoned dried dates, finely chopped', '1 tbsp light muscovado sugar', '50 g (1¾ oz) barley flakes', '50 g (1¾ oz) self-raising wholemeal flour', '½ tsp baking powder', '2 tbsp sunflower oil', '4 tbsp apple juice']
